”이라면서도 “완성차 업체들이 관세 리스크를 최소화하기 위해 미국 현지 생산 배터리를 사용할 경우에는 기회가 될 수 있다”고 전했다.","url":"https://www.seoul.co.kr/news/economy/industry/2026/05/05/20260505500097","published_at":"2026-05-05T18:00:10","sentiment":"neutral","is_new":true}],"disclosures":[{"date":"2026-04-30T09:42:29","title":"[기재정정]연결재무제표기준영업(잠정)실적(공정공시)              ","url":"https://dart.fss.or.kr/dsaf001/main.do?rcpNo=20260430800165","is_new":false},{"date":"2026-04-29T10:14:59","title":"[기재정정]유형자산처분결정(종속회사의주요경영사항)              ","url":"https://dart.fss.or.kr/dsaf001/main.do?rcpNo=20260429800214","is_new":false},{"date":"2026-04-28T16:33:14","title":"특수관계인으로부터부동산임차","url":"https://dart.fss.or.kr/dsaf001/main.do?rcpNo=20260428000648","is_new":false},{"date":"2026-04-28T14:43:05","title":"공정거래자율준수프로그램운영현황(안내공시)              ","url":"https://dart.fss.or.kr/dsaf001/main.do?rcpNo=20260428800413","is_new":false}],"reports":[],"consensus":{"Q":[{"date":"2026-05-04","term":"Q","period":"2026년 2분기","value":203130000.0,"previous":null,"change_pct":null,"is_new":false},{"date":"2026-04-30","term":"Q","period":"2026년 2분기","value":94617647.05882,"previous":203130000.0,"change_pct":-53.42,"is_new":false},{"date":"2026-04-29","term":"Q","period":"2026년 2분기","value":98533333.33333,"previous":94617647.05882,"change_pct":4.14,"is_new":false},{"date":"2026-04-08","term":"Q","period":"2026년 2분기","value":105760000.0,"previous":98533333.33333,"change_pct":7.33,"is_new":false},{"date":"2026-04-07","term":"Q","period":"2026년 2분기","value":125410000.0,"previous":105760000.0,"change_pct":18.58,"is_new":false}],"Y":[{"date":"2026-05-04","term":"Y","period":"2026년","value":1217528571.42857,"previous":null,"change_pct":null,"is_new":false},{"date":"2026-04-30","term":"Y","period":"2026년","value":1145055555.55556,"previous":1217528571.42857,"change_pct":-5.95,"is_new":false},{"date":"2026-04-29","term":"Y","period":"2026년","value":1227595652.17391,"previous":1145055555.55556,"change_pct":7.21,"is_new":false},{"date":"2026-04-08","term":